-- FACTBOX: Jobs gloom for 2009
-- 
-- Wed Feb 18, 2009 9:23am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/18/us-economy-jobcuts-factbox-sb-idUSTRE51H2IJ20090218

 

 (Reuters) - General Motors Corp and Chrysler LLC said on Tuesday they would make huge cuts to their workforces, in restructuring plans submitted to the U.S. government as part of the terms of a federal bailout. 

